{"tid":2397083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強：《國安法》案件調查及取證全由警方自行處理　拘捕民主派人士並非展示下馬威","createTime":"2021-02-06T06:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T09:06:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb9dfe8953aeb350b4c3c46061a1c0765a5dc9a","tid":2397083,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"警務處處長鄧炳強表示，社會存在危害國家安全的行為，至今有97人涉嫌違反《香港國安法》被捕，這些案件的調查及取證等工作都由警方自行處理，他又否認大規模拘捕行動是要向民主派展示下馬威。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強又說，與反修例示威相關的未成年被捕人士，只有19人接受了警司警誡，他認為與網上一些言論有關，被捕人較少說話及承認罪行，未能以警司警誡處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574454-20210206.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574454-20210206.htm&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=5bc4a23b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574454-20210206.htm&h=1c6215af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574454-20210206.htm</a>"},{"pid":"20dce56a7be69fbf608e1214a7d1d1aa675f4622","tid":2397083,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yfxx4py.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyfxx4py.gif&h=92405386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fac9d0ec521a1c17332e2dae1a6f886dd662e28","tid":2397083,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20dce56a7be69fbf608e1214a7d1d1aa675f4622","tid":2397083,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yfxx4py.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyfxx4py.gif&h=92405386&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ad0cde625351b0cffcc9221b703